# simplification for converting files to mobi format

This repo does not contains convertor it self.

You can find it on official page, where you have to agree with their terms of use

https://www.amazon.com/gp/feature.html?ie=UTF8&docId=1000765211

This app is only a primitive bridge for it.

To use it, you have to download kindlegen app and put executable file into `exe` folder.

app.js accepts only one optional argument - port (default: 4500)